chrony|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
chrony: chrony (An NTP client/server)
chrony:
chrony: A client/server for the Network Time Protocol, this program keeps your
chrony: computer's clock accurate. It was specially designed to support
chrony: systems with intermittent internet connections, but it also works well
chrony: in permanently connected environments. It can use also hardware
chrony: reference clocks, system real-time clock or manual input as time
chrony: references.
chrony:
chrony: http://chrony.tuxfamily.org
